    {
      "id": "db023e76_68c9dc45",
      "file_path": "packages/policy-clamp-docker/src/main/docker/controlloop-runtime.sh",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "For the below command \nENTRYPOINT [ \"./controlloop-runtime.sh $POLICY_HOME/etc/ClRuntimeParameters.json\" ]\n\nI tried printing the Total, $0, $1, $2, $3 them as below\n\npolicy-controlloop-runtime        | Print number of total entries in command: 2\npolicy-controlloop-runtime        | Print 0 is : ./controlloop-runtime.sh\npolicy-controlloop-runtime        | Print 1 is : -c\npolicy-controlloop-runtime        | Print 2 is : /opt/app/policy/clamp/etc/onappf/config/ClRuntimeParameters.json\npolicy-controlloop-runtime        | Print 3 is : \npolicy-controlloop-runtime        | Policy clamp config file: /opt/app/policy/clamp/etc/onappf/config/ClRuntimeParameters.json\n\nAs i need $2 for CONFIG_FILE, i am leaving it as-it-is. Please let me know, if this interpretation is'nt correct.",
      "author": {
