      "file_path": "packages/policy-clamp-docker/src/main/docker/controlloop-runtime.sh",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "ah, in that case, need to decide which it's going to be: stick with the form in ENTRYPOINT, or stick with the form in docker-compose.  If the former, then need to remove the second \"-c\" from docker-compose and change $1 to $2.  OTOH, if the latter, then need to add \"-c\" to the line in ENTRYPOINT and leave the $2 as is.\n\nHowever, if sticking with the latter, then I would suggest beefing up the shell script(s) to look explicitly for \"-c\" rather than assuming it's there.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 811,
        "name": "Jim Hahn",
        "display_name": null,
