    {
      "id": "c376d08d_4fe0ffe5",
      "file_path": "packages/policy-clamp-docker/src/main/docker/dcae-participant.sh",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": null,
      "message": "<Question> so I assume that the participant is now completely self contained in app.jar? \n<Answer> Yes. Participant code is completely contained in app.jar, this is being done in policy-clamp-docker/pom.xml with assembly tag while building Participant docker images using docker-maven-plugin.\n\n<Question> Can logback.xml still be overridden?  \n<Answer> I have added another dependencySet in policy-clamp-docker/pom.xml to build policy-participant.tar.gz which contains an etc directory\nwhich inturn contains logback files and ssl. By this, these can become available in /opt/app/policy/clamp/etc (Or $POLICY_HOME/etc) just like\nany other policy containers.\n\n$docker exec -it dcae-participant ls ../etc\nClRuntimeParameters.json          logback.xml\nDcaeParticipantParameters.json    onappf\nPolicyParticipantParameters.json  ssl\nlogback-default.xml\n\n<dependencySet>\n    <includes>\n        <include>org.onap.policy.clamp:policy-clamp-tarball</include>\n    </includes>\n    <outputDirectory>/lib</outputDirectory>\n    <outputFileNameMapping>policy-participant.tar.gz</outputFileNameMapping>\n</dependencySet>\n\n<Question> We normally put config files in \"etc\", not \"config\".  Does Spring force it to be \"config\"?\n<Answer> Yes, It looks for configuration in config directory in the order specified according to the documentation.\n$ docker exec -it dcae-participant pwd\n/opt/app/policy/clamp/bin\n$ docker exec -it dcae-participant ls ..\nbin     config  etc https://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/1.5.6.RELEASE/reference/html/boot-features-external-config.html#boot-features-external-config-application-property-files",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7504,
        "name": "Sirisha Manchikanti",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "sirisha.manchikanti@est.tech",
        "username": "Sirisha_Manchikanti"
      },
      "updated": "2021-06-16 13:54:06.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "cd1bbb65_e8cacbb7",
      "unresolved": false
    },
